title: Stars on Mars
overview: An out-of-this-world new unscripted series, in which household names trade in their possessions, status and glamourous lifestyles on Earth for an insane and hilarious summer on 'Mars'. Their mission? To be suited up with no space to go, as they colonize, compete and conquer their new galaxy surroundings, until there is just one 'celebronaut' left standing.
